00:00:52.889 --> 00:00:56.829
The 1950s and 1960s were a golden

00:00:56.879 --> 00:00:59.559
era for new kitchen gadgets.

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:02.839
Armed with disposable income and

00:01:02.839 --> 00:01:05.559
a lust for convenience, American

00:01:05.559 --> 00:01:08.559
consumers snapped up microwaves,

00:01:08.809 --> 00:01:11.279
fridge freezers, and Tupperwares.

00:01:11.899 --> 00:01:14.399
