00:01:14.469 --> 00:01:16.459
plastic forks and knives would mean

00:01:16.469 --> 00:01:18.669
families would never have to wash up

00:01:18.669 --> 00:01:21.939
again; you’d unwrap a new set of cutlery

00:01:21.939 --> 00:01:24.539
with every meal, then simply throw

00:01:24.539 --> 00:01:26.289
it away when you were done with it.

00:01:27.269 --> 00:01:28.639
And there was more.

00:01:29.489 --> 00:01:32.089
One company, DuPont, produced

00:01:32.119 --> 00:01:33.919
a magical type of frying pan

00:01:34.149 --> 00:01:35.815
that food wouldn’t stick to.

00:01:36.899 --> 00:01:39.119
No longer would your morning fried

00:01:39.119 --> 00:01:41.299
egg get stuck to the pan and burn,

00:01:41.709 --> 00:01:43.759
no longer would you have to scrub

00:01:43.789 --> 00:01:46.179
