00:01:53.219 --> 00:01:55.839
The adverts boasted of “saving you

00:01:55.839 --> 00:01:58.289
a load of dirty work”, and showed

00:01:58.289 --> 00:02:00.529
quite how easily even the toughest

00:02:00.529 --> 00:02:03.369
of foods could be simply wiped away.

00:02:04.279 --> 00:02:05.779
Unsurprisingly, they

00:02:05.779 --> 00:02:07.689
were an immediate hit.

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:10.059
By the early 1960s, these

00:02:10.319 --> 00:02:12.209
pans were everywhere.

00:02:13.319 --> 00:02:16.689
